Education Requirement: Undergraduate or above, major in Statistics, Mathematics, Computer Science, Information Management, Economics or related fields is preferred;

Skill Requirement: Proficient in SQL, able to independently write complex query statements to complete data extraction and analysis; Master basic data analysis methods and have basic data sensitivity;

Language Requirement: Proficient in English, able to read English technical documents fluently and have basic English communication skills;

Internship Time: Able to intern 5 days a week, internship period of no less than 3 months, priority given to those who can intern stably for a long time;

Personal Qualities: Serious and responsible at work, careful and rigorous, with good logical thinking ability and team spirit, proactive and willing to learn new skills.

